name: Mitt Konto Should Be Visible and Have HTTP Status Code STATUS_OK (200)
fullName: Test Cases.External Dependencies.Mitt Konto Should Be Visible and Have HTTP Status Code STATUS_OK (200)
description:
This test checks whether the JLT Mitt Konto is visible and when clicked, returns an HTTP status code of 200 (OK).
Steps:
1. Check if JLT Mitt Konto is visible
2. Send a GET request to JLT Mitt Konto
3. Verify that the received HTTP status code is 200.
